20</category><category>deck sanding</category><category>grit progression</category><description>Engineer-tested guide to the best grit for deck sanding before staining, with abrasive science, tool choices, and proven sanding sequences.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining"&gt;Best Grit for Deck Sanding Before Staining&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Saturday morning sunlight hits the deck and it looks like two decks at once: the cheerful gathering place you want for the season ahead, and the weathered surface you’ve come to ignore—grayed, patchy stain, a couple of raised splinters in the traffic lane from the back door. If you’ve decided to refresh it, you’ll run into a deceptively technical question right away: what’s the best grit for deck sanding before staining? As a product engineer who field-tests tools and abrasives, I’ve learned that grit choice isn’t a cosmetic preference—it’s a performance variable that decides how well stain bonds, how evenly it soaks, and how long your finish resists UV and foot traffic. In deck sanding, you aren’t polishing furniture; you’re tuning the surface profile to balance penetration and smoothness.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding/cards/instagram/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding/cards/instagram/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/best-grit-for-deck-sanding-before-staining-deck-sanding/cards/instagram/best-grit-for-d